IMAPAccount mailbox
Host imap.mailbox.org
UserCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.authinfo.gpg | awk -F ' ' '/mailbox/ { print $(NF-2); exit; }'"
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.authinfo.gpg | awk -F ' ' '/mailbox/ { print $(NF); exit; }'"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore mailbox-remote
account mailbox

MaildirStore mailbox-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/mailbox/
Inbox ~/.mail/mailbox/Inbox

Channel mailbox
Far :mailbox-remote:
Near :mailbox-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
Sync All